<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't looking!</font>

236
00:16:38,180 --> 00:16:39,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?!</font>

237
00:16:40,190 --> 00:16:41,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm fine.</font>

238
00:16:42,750 --> 00:16:45,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm truly sorry, really!</font>

239
00:16:45,810 --> 00:16:47,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right.</font>

240
00:16:49,430 --> 00:16:51,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That startled me.</font>

241
00:16:51,670 --> 00:16:54,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought someone had pushed me.</font>

242
00:16:55,030 --> 00:16:57,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're my hero, huh, Aqua-kun?</font>

243
00:16:57,980 --> 00:17:00,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whenever I'm in trouble, 
