244
00:17:03,970 --> 00:17:04,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

245
00:17:05,390 --> 00:17:09,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Given what's in the news now, 
you shouldn't be out and about.</font>

246
00:17:09,980 --> 00:17:10,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akane.</font>

247
00:17:13,270 --> 00:17:15,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't do anything dangerous.</font>

248
00:17:18,100 --> 00:17:19,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you say that?</font>

249
00:17:28,170 --> 00:17:29,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why...</font>

250
00:17:30,430 --> 00:17:32,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you here?</font>

251
00:17:34,830 --> 00:17:36,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have work today.</font>

252
00:17:37,350 --> 00:17:40,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you just got out of school, 
why aren't you in uniform?</font>

253
00:17:40,630 --> 00:17:42,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean, 
"Don't do anything dangerous"?</font>

254
00:17:42,670 --> 00:17:47,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're talking like you 
know what I'm doing.</font>

255
00:17:49,670 --> 00:17:51,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really are too smart 
for your own good.</font>

256
00:18:10,150 --> 00:18:13,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aqua-kun... This isn't okay.</font>

257
00:18:14,770 --> 00:18:17,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've crossed the line.</font>

258
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:25,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When did you start bugging me?</font>

259
00:18:27,760 --> 00:18:30,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not long after <i>Love for Real</i>.</font>

260
00:18:31,130 --> 00:18:33,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you might find 
a lead of some sort,</font>

261
00:18:34,430 --> 00:18:38,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I wanted to track you if you 
made contact with the mastermind.</font>

262
00:18:42,360 --> 00:18:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess I made the right call back then.</font>

263
00:18:47,540 --> 00:18:52,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought we were building 
a good relationship as equals.</font>

264
00:18:53,840 --> 00:18:57,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I was wrong, wasn't I?</font>

265
00:18:59,070 --> 00:19:02,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you trusted me more than this.</font>

266
00:19:03,920 --> 00:19:06,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know about your situation.</font>

267
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:11,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've always said I'd help you, haven't I?</font>

268
00:19:14,120 --> 00:19:16,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'd just asked me,</font>

269
00:19:16,140 --> 00:19:18,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would've worn hundreds of these for you!</font>

270
00:19:18,550 --> 00:19:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not an object or your sniffer dog! 
I'm a human being!</font>

271
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:25,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this shows that you 
don't see me as one!</font>

272
00:19:27,770 --> 00:19:31,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'd only asked, I would've gladly...</font>

273
00:19:31,020 --> 00:19:31,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a lie.</font>

274
00:19:35,190 --> 00:19:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akane, if you'd known about this,</font>

275
00:19:39,940 --> 00:19:42,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you definitely would've done 
something to counter it.</font>

276
00:19:47,140 --> 00:19:48,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This says it all.</font>

277
00:19:48,940 --> 00:19:52,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You found information about my dad,</font>

278
00:19:52,940 --> 00:19:54,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you were intending 
to settle things yourself.</font>

279
00:19:54,990 --> 00:19:57,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't! I was just...</font>

280
00:19:57,880 --> 00:19:59,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Explain this, then.</font>

281
00:20:01,390 --> 00:20:04,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What exactly were you 
going to do with this?</font>

282
00:20:06,450 --> 00:20:09,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was planning to talk to him.</font>

283
00:20:09,340 --> 00:20:13,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just, anything could happen. 
He's a murderer and all.</font>

284
00:20:13,750 --> 00:20:16,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was only going to use it 
as a last resort.</font>

285
00:20:17,800 --> 00:20:19,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I brought it to protect myself—</font>

286
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:19,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akane.</font>

287
00:20:20,990 --> 00:20:22,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay out of this.</font>

288
00:20:23,830 --> 00:20:25,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll stop GPS tracking you.</font>

289
00:20:26,910 --> 00:20:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'll get out of your life forever.</font>

290
00:20:33,800 --> 00:20:35,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So stop putting yourself in danger.</font>

291
00:20:40,170 --> 00:20:45,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You say you were only using me, 
yet you're letting me down gently.</font>

292
00:20:52,960 --> 00:20:57,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If only you'd asked me to go with you... 
I'd even follow you into hell.</font>

293
00:20:58,700 --> 00:21:02,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would never take you there.</font>

294
00:21:03,230 --> 00:21:04,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go on my own.</font>

295
00:21:06,340 --> 00:21:09,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... You've made up your mind, huh?</font>

296
00:21:11,710 --> 00:21:13,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's just one thing 
I want to say to you.</font>

297
00:21:16,550 --> 00:21:19,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You chose the wrong path, Aqua-kun.</font>

298
00:21:20,710 --> 00:21:21,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trust me, I know.</font>

299
00:21:29,360 --> 00:21:33,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So there's no stopping you anymore?</font>

300
00:21:35,630 --> 00:21:39,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I couldn't save you.</font>

301
00:21:42,320 --> 00:21:44,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't care if it was arrogant of me.</font>

302
00:21:45,510 --> 00:21:48,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted so badly to save you!</font>

303
00:21:52,620 --> 00:21:53,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is for the best.</i></font>

304
00:21:54,060 --> 00:21:58,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now Akane won't be in harm's way 
