305
00:22:00,170 --> 00:22:02,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The happy times are over.</i></font>

306
00:22:03,370 --> 00:22:05,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no going back for me.</i></font>

307
00:22:05,720 --> 00:22:07,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll have to follow this path 
